{"tid":2229130,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"呢度有冇公屋上蓋膠","createTime":"2020-10-04T07:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T09:40:23.000Z","uid":367101,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"65f21acbcaf413f55da14a96eb997b8d3623dd41","tid":2229130,"uid":367101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:20:36.000Z","msg":"當然我梗係唔中意住公屋 不過住緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係呢一年都發現香港有d公屋樓下黐住個商場<br />\n甚至連埋巴士總站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總係覺得呢種感覺好特別 同埋佢方便<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如寶達邨達祥樓佢連住個商場同巴士總站<br />\n 另一邊嘅出口仲要一出五步路就可以上巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sOEaPuF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsOEaPuF.jpg&h=8c052478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTLmbLb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTLmbLb.png&h=1748886a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有安定邨定祥樓同友愛邨愛勇樓<br />\n定祥一出門口就有巴士站 仲有七條線直出九龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n愛勇一落就係輕鐵站可以去晒屯元天<br />\n不過成個地方咁cup住好迷宮...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋好多狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kLqEHQY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkLqEHQY.png&h=762ca2e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ebwo9vZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Febwo9vZ.png&h=0eb5c4b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有富秦邨君秦樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌那星地下冇入口嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要喺商場搭lift上5樓先到大堂<br />\n但係佢個感覺好特別 好似去咗天水圍咁<br />\n不過特別多力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時屯門一個月都見唔到10個 <br />\n呢度10分鐘就10個<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pmRMnTk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpmRMnTk.jpg&h=5683b592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oWURyZ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoWURyZ2.jpg&h=55ccc66d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/94wXuyq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F94wXuyq.jpg&h=29cb76d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有 蝴蝶邨蝶心樓同隔離都係連住商場嘅蝶翎樓<br />\n全港唯一嘅梯級Y型大廈(官方叫舊長型大廈)<br />\n越高層伙數越少 <br />\n不過最低幾層一梯68伙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但全部細單位 <br />\n佢仲有一個係全港最大嘅單層街市 不過我唔覺得好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oicjHVh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoicjHVh.png&h=1990e34d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rCNDd1Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrCNDd1Y.png&h=3789a0be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實其他區仲有冇咁樣商場上面係住人嘅公屋<br />\n好似唔多覺咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"890ee2306740113f81da3d90349ad56b8b6f4fff","tid":2229130,"uid":71508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"舒服，方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n私樓冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恨唔到架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c890685784ddb27cae03bfa4dc8f3ff64a742c71","tid":2229130,"uid":9193,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:27:42.000Z","msg":"我因為工作需要成日周圍走<br />\n發覺好多公屋配套比私人樓更好<br />\n有啲私人樓甚至乜都冇要過隔離屋村商場"},{"pid":"576047adec81af17a52ed641a47a2061ef7bd953","tid":2229130,"uid":218551,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:37:48.000Z","msg":"安定友愛都吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n商場又細又垃圾，條邨勁舊又多蝗多廢老，又無社區設施，體育館個出入口都閪過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錯，搭車出去係方便，但只係街邊站頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日曬雨淋仲要食塵<br />\n<br />\n利申　工作關係係個邊出入過一年"},{"pid":"85abfc5a530eaae54459e46963ccad1ec7131dc4","tid":2229130,"uid":373220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:46:38.000Z","msg":"太多廢老、大陸人同痴線佬<br />\n咁都吹奏"},{"pid":"df72aeee43565ce75f5205dee4298fade2424ada","tid":2229130,"uid":208270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"寶達一定要幫襯撈得店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ff8417bb395fb5ef77fce666fc7789db19cf9b","tid":2229130,"uid":300420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec41b7060ef613f0de39463dafd55cb34241b379","tid":2229130,"uid":31521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:52:19.000Z","msg":"有朋友住嗰座癡住商場<br />\n好鬼多老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後屋企兩隻貓會幫手捉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31bc720ec3afc64e9c4b90b11cf0bb2a5839b262","tid":2229130,"uid":67006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:03:28.000Z","msg":"同你一樣<br />\n舊式公屋既屋村設計有種魔力<br />\n成日想走入去睇下個屋苑LAYOUT<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0795fc691763dc0f91d274d3e5341fc45aaee9ee","tid":2229130,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:11:11.000Z","msg":"我長沙灣站出口返到屋企30秒唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6e7fd85c29d571d35d5965208384c0565770e5","tid":2229130,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"寶達邨個格局好恐怖"},{"pid":"08f0181bd174de8c1eadd2b17cffa7bd610d77a5","tid":2229130,"uid":45827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"寶達個交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96115c8608c2b701c384641b160d75f9ad96a4e3","tid":2229130,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:04:26.000Z","msg":"太和？<br />\n有幾座起喺商場上面，癡住黨鐵站"},{"pid":"1e332ea50f021d6bf727ce6565ada0f5e5664a5e","tid":2229130,"uid":367101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da6e7fd85c29d571d35d5965208384c0565770e5","tid":2229130,"uid":48277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T10:54:54.000Z","msg":"寶達邨個格局好恐怖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T12:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />對行人unfriendly"},{"pid":"818734687e7223e24975676cf558744803ce3c71","tid":2229130,"uid":251328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"576047adec81af17a52ed641a47a2061ef7bd953","tid":2229130,"uid":218551,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T07:37:48.000Z","msg":"安定友愛都吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n商場又細又垃圾，條邨勁舊又多蝗多廢老，又無社區設施，體育館個出入口都閪過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無錯，搭車出去係方便，但只係街邊站頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日曬雨淋仲要食塵<br />\n<br />\n利申　工作關係係個邊出入過一年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:26:04.000Z","msg":"友愛反而叉仔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似變咗條蝻亞邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1120ee8836117f2c00910f0dc3c0c470ded6467f","tid":2229130,"uid":378926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0795fc691763dc0f91d274d3e5341fc45aaee9ee","tid":2229130,"uid":140726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T09:11:11.000Z","msg":"我長沙灣站出口返到屋企30秒唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T09:40:23.000Z","msg":"元州邨？"}]}